### PR-014

**Title**: Streaming observability — TTFT, token/sec, and stall detection for SSE responses
**Problem**: The streaming code in `src/sse/` and `open-sse/handlers/responsesHandler.ts` has no per-token timing. Users can't tell whether a slow response is the model or the network.
**Solution**:
- For each SSE chunk, capture `ttft_ms`, `tokens_so_far`, `chunk_bytes`, `delta_ms`, and compute instantaneous `tokens_per_sec`.
- Emit metrics: `omniroute_streaming_ttft_seconds{provider,model,quantile}`, `omniroute_streaming_tokens_per_second{provider,model}`, `omniroute_streaming_stall_total{provider,model,stall_ms}`.
- Live Stream Inspector: a UI `src/app/(dashboard)/observability/streams/page.tsx` (read-only) that mirrors a live stream with per-token timing on a timeline.
- Files affected: `src/sse/parser.ts:1-200` (instrumented), `open-sse/handlers/responsesHandler.ts:1-200` (instrumented), `src/lib/observability/streaming.ts` (new, 230 LOC), `src/lib/observability/metrics.ts:1-380` (extend), `src/app/(dashboard)/observability/streams/page.tsx` (new, 200 LOC), `src/app/(dashboard)/observability/streams/LiveTimeline.tsx` (new, 220 LOC), `src/shared/components/charts/StreamTimeline.tsx` (new, 130 LOC), `src/app/api/observability/streams/route.ts` (new, 100 LOC), `tests/unit/observability/streaming.test.ts` (new, 220 LOC), `tests/e2e/observability/streams.spec.ts` (new, 130 LOC), `docs/observability/11-streaming.md` (new, 70 LOC).
**Test plan**: Synthetic SSE source at 50 tokens/sec, assert metric. Inject a 2-second stall, assert stall counter increments.
**Risk**: Med — instrumenting the hot streaming path; must be allocation-free.
**Estimate**: L

